OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FThere is "serious concern" over fuel
OL,7,Fsupplies for Irish emergency service
OL,8,Fvehicles after three days of protests
OL,9,Fover petrol and diesel costs arising
OL,10,Fout of the war in the Middle East.
OL,12,FHauliers and agricultural contractors
OL,13,Fbegan protests at various sites around
OL,14,Fthe country on Tuesday by implementing
OL,15,Fslow-moving convoys on motorways,
OL,16,Frestricting access to Dublin's busiest
OL,17,Fstreets and blockading fuel depots
OL,18,Fthat supply half the country.
OL,26,@nD@JOUnD@ZO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FParticipants, many of whom have slept
OL,7,Fovernight in their vehicles as the
OL,8,Fdemonstration entered a third day on
OL,9,FThursday, say they will continue their
OL,10,Faction until they receive engagement
OL,11,Ffrom Government or are physically
OL,12,Fremoved.
OL,14,FThe latter option has become more of a
OL,15,Fpossibility after Irish police
OL,16,Fformally requested the assistance of
OL,17,Fthe Defence Forces in responding to
OL,18,Fwhat Ireland's premier called an "act
OL,19,Fof national sabotage".
OL,26,@zD@bOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FIn one of the first acts of
OL,7,Fenforcement, social media footage late
OL,8,Fon Thursday showed An Garda Siochana
OL,9,Fwarning some protesters they could be
OL,10,Farrested if they did not disperse from
OL,11,Fan area near Rosslare Europort.
OL,13,FThe development came as a spokesman
OL,14,Ffor a concurrent blockade in Dublin
OL,15,Fcity centre said there had been a
OL,16,F"breakthrough", and claimed protest
OL,17,Fparticipants would be attending a
OL,18,Fmeeting with Government on Friday that
OL,19,Fwas originally scheduled for official
OL,20,Fnational representative bodies.
OL,26,@xD@AOUxD@NO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FJames Geoghegan told RTE's Prime Time
OL,7,Fthey had "a list of demands going into
OL,8,FGovernment tomorrow" ` with a
OL,9,Fcoalition spokesman stating that who
OL,10,F"nationally and democratically
OL,11,Fconstituted bodies choose to bring
OL,12,Falong with them is a matter for them".
OL,14,FThe widespread disruption arose out of
OL,15,Fseparate but co-ordinated protests
OL,16,Faround Ireland's major cities over
OL,17,Fdemands for further cuts to fuel
OL,18,Fcosts, which have soared as a result
OL,19,Fof the war in the Middle East and the
OL,20,Fimpact on supplies passing through the
OL,21,FStrait of Hormuz.
OL,26,@oD@JOUpD@TO]rD@AOUtD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30305
