CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FJust over two weeks ago, Ireland's
OL,7,Fruling coalition signed off on a range
OL,8,Fof measures to reduce fuel costs,
OL,9,Fincluding a temporary excise duty
OL,10,Freduction for motor fuels, expansion
OL,11,Fof the diesel rebate scheme for
OL,12,Fhauliers and bus operators, and an
OL,13,Fextension of the fuel allowance.
OL,15,FIt saw an effective reduction of 17
OL,16,Fcent for petrol, 22 cent for diesel,
OL,17,Fand five cent for marked gas oil
OL,18,F(green diesel) ` but the savings were
OL,19,Flargely eroded as the war waged on.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FProtesters have restricted access to a
OL,7,Fmajor oil refinery in Whitegate, Co
OL,8,FCork, as well as fuel depots in Galway
OL,9,FCity and Foynes, Co Limerick.
OL,11,FOther action saw major disruption to
OL,12,Ftraffic around Dublin city as well as
OL,13,Fa complete blockage of key routes in
OL,14,Fthe capital, including O'Connell
OL,15,FStreet.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FIt has raised concern over panic
OL,7,Fbuying at forecourts, some of which
OL,8,Fhave ran out of fuel, as well as
OL,9,Fimpacts on emergency services and
OL,10,Fdeliveries of key supplies for animal
OL,11,Fwelfare on farms.
OL,13,FOn Thursday morning, Ireland's Justice
OL,14,FMinister Jim O'Callaghan said the
OL,15,FDefence Forces would assist the police
OL,16,Fservice, An Garda Siochana, in
OL,17,Fremoving vehicles from the blockade.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FHe said: "The blocking of critical
OL,7,Fnational infrastructure will not be
OL,8,Fpermitted to continue and the
OL,9,Fassistance of the Defence Forces has
OL,10,Fbeen requested."
OL,12,FThey military has four heavy-lift
OL,13,Frecovery trucks to help clear trucks
OL,14,Fand tractors and it is understood that
OL,15,Fassistance will be limited to these
OL,16,Ftrucks and the personnel required to
OL,17,Foperate them.
OL,26,@nD@JOUrD@PO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
