OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FDefence Minister Helen McEntee told
OL,7,Freporters at the Curragh Camp that the
OL,8,FDefence Forces intervention was "never
OL,9,Fa first resort".
OL,11,FHowever, she said: "It cannot be the
OL,12,Fcase that individuals decide that they
OL,13,Fare going to blockade parts of the
OL,14,Fcountry and stop people from going
OL,15,Fabout their business."
OL,26,@pD@aOUqD@OO]sD@TOUwD@VO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G9/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
