CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FIn a statement to the media at Garda
OL,7,Fheadquarters in Dublin, Deputy
OL,8,FCommissioner Shawna Coxon said gardai
OL,9,Fare "moving to an enforcement phase"
OL,10,Funless protesters "desist and
OL,11,Fdisperse".
OL,13,FShe added: "An Garda Siochana is
OL,14,Fadvising protesters to immediately
OL,15,Fcease blockades of such critical
OL,16,Fnational infrastructure or face the
OL,17,Ffull rigours of the law."
OL,26,@qD@EOUqD@dO]rD@SOUsD@IO]uD@LOUyD@YO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G10/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FTaoiseach Micheal Martin said the
OL,7,F"Government had to act" over the
OL,8,Fblockades of fuel centres but told RTE
OL,9,Fhe did not expect violence if the army
OL,10,Fand gardai moved in.
OL,12,FMr O'Callaghan said protesters are
OL,13,Fbeing "manipulated" by "outside
OL,14,Factors" including right-wing activist
OL,15,FTommy Robinson.
OL,17,FHe said there were "many outside
OL,18,Factors" who "really want to damage
OL,19,FIreland as a country", manipulating
OL,20,Fprotesters online.
OL,26,@oD@AOUoD@WO]uD@GOUuD@SO]uD@XOUvD@GO]yD@
OL,26,ATOUzD@GO]zD@MOU{D@UO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G11/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30312
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FThe continued blockade means Ireland
OL,7,F"cannot continue to maintain fuel
OL,8,Fsupply to forecourts", according to a
OL,9,Fleading industry representative, who
OL,10,Fwarned that shortages were being felt
OL,11,Fmost in the west.
OL,13,FFuels for Ireland chief executive
OL,14,FKevin McPartland said the number of
OL,15,Fforecourts that had run dry was in the
OL,16,F"low double digits" but warned that it
OL,17,Fwould get "much, much worse" by the
OL,18,Fhour.
OL,26,@oD@AOUpD@UO]xD@AOUxD@SO]yD@KOUyD@\O]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G12/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30313
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FAsked when fuel would run out at
OL,7,Fservice stations, he told RTE radio:
OL,8,F"We can't model it because we're not
OL,9,Fhaving normal levels of demand ` panic
OL,10,Fbuying has absolutely taken hold."
OL,12,FHe warned that "real significant life-
OL,13,Fdeath problems are going to be caused"
OL,14,Fwith fuel supplies to emergency
OL,15,Fservice vehicles also under threat.
OL,17,FIreland's emergency planning group
OL,18,Fechoed the comments with "serious
OL,19,Fconcern", saying there may be an
OL,20,Fimpacts on availability for some
OL,21,Femergency services.
OL,26,@pD@AOUrD@bO]tD@POUuD@fO]zD@ZOU{D@HO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G13/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30314
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FThe National Emergency Co-ordination
OL,7,FGroup (NECG) said Ireland's overall
OL,8,Ffuel supplies remain "robust and
OL,9,Fresilient", but added that blockades
OL,10,Fare continuing to cause significant
OL,11,Fdisruption for the public, to supply
OL,12,Fchains and vital services, and public
OL,13,Ftransport.
OL,15,FIreland's Health Service Executive
OL,16,F(HSE) said the disruption is causing
OL,17,Fpeople to miss medical appointments
OL,18,Fand is impacting the provision of home
OL,19,Fcare and critical care, such as
OL,20,Fdialysis and cancer treatment.
OL,26,@pD@VOUqD@JO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G14/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30315
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FThe HSE also warned that the blockades
OL,7,Fcould disrupt the time-sensitive
OL,8,Fdelivery of key medicines and medical
OL,9,Fdevices.
OL,11,FThe NECG said the obstruction of key
OL,12,Froutes from ports is threatening the
OL,13,Fprovision of animal feed supplies,
OL,14,Ffertiliser and other vital materials,
OL,15,Fresulting in potential animal welfare
OL,16,Fissues and a threat to livelihoods in
OL,17,Fthe agriculture sector.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G15/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,304,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30316
SC,0016
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,FProtesters in Dublin city centre said
OL,7,Fthey had nominated "three or four"
OL,8,Fspokespeople they want to meet
OL,9,FGovernment leaders.
OL,11,FHowever, speaking on RTE radio's
OL,12,FMorning Ireland show, one of them,
OL,13,FJohn Dallon, said he does not speak
OL,14,Ffor the protesters blocking fuel
OL,15,Fdepots: "I'm here on the streets of
OL,16,FDublin, I have no voice as regards
OL,17,Fwhat's happening down the country as
OL,18,Fregards blocking up ports.
OL,26,@oD@TOUoD@bO]wD@IOU
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                   G16/17
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
