PN,30317
SC,0017
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F303A1775782987
OL,3,CIrish fuel protests causing 'serious
OL,4,Cconcern' for emergency services
OL,6,F"What's happening down there is out of
OL,7,Fmy hands, I have no control over what
OL,8,Fhappens."
OL,26,@nD@AOUpD@IO]
